-- Merck Paid 3,468 Claims Over Deaths Blamed on Vioxx Painkiller, Judge Told
-- Allen Johnson
-- 2010-07-27T19:56:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/merck-paid-3-468-claims-over-deaths-blamed-on-vioxx-painkiller-judge-told.html

          
          
             Merck & Co. paid claims to the
families of 3,468 users of its Vioxx painkiller who died of
heart attacks or strokes, a claims administrator told a judge
today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
